Text:
Ah yes, the holy grail of calendars the Pirelli... Resolutions are too low to do anything with them but a nice upload at least to get a glimpse at some of those pics anyways.
Thank you...

Yeah. The quality is not the best on some of them, and some are pretty good, and some are average, but I couldn't find better for most of them. For only 72 Mb it's worth the download if only to see what they are like.
The quality of the previews is about typical of all of them. A few years are worse. A few are better. Remember some of these pics are almost 50 years old.
